## REGRAS CRГҚTICAS DO PROJETO

### TypeScript
- вң… `strict: true` sempre
- вң… Zero `any`
- вң… Use `unknown` + type guards
- вқҢ Sem `// @ts-ignore` ou `@ts-expect-error`

### Naming
- Services: `*Service.ts` (profileService, chatService)
- Screens: `*Screen.tsx` (HomeScreen, ChatScreen)
- Components: `*Component.tsx` ou `*Organism.tsx` (MaternalCard, EmotionalPrompt)
- Hooks: `use*` (useAIRouting, useEmotionTracking)

### Logging
- вң… Use `logger.info()`, `logger.error()` (from utils/logger.ts)
- вқҢ Nunca `console.log`

### Styling
- вң… Use design tokens (`src/theme/tokens.ts`)
- вң… NativeWind (Tailwind) para consistency
- вқҢ Hardcoded colors/sizes
- вқҢ StyleSheet.create (use tokens directly)

### IA Integrations
- вң… Sempre rote via `llmRouter.ts`
- вң… Log cada chamada (provider, tokens, cost)
- вң… Fallback automГЎtico
- вң… Crisis detection antes de qualquer resposta
- вқҢ DiagnГіstico mГ©dico sem disclaimer

### Supabase
- вң… RLS policies em TODAS as tables
- вң… Migrations versionadas
- вң… EdgeFunctions para lГіgica complexa
- вң… AsyncStorage para offline cache
- вқҢ Queries sem Гӯndices (perf killer)

### Testing
- вң… Jest + React Native Testing Library
- вң… MГӯnimo 40% MVP, 60% Phase 2, 80% final
- вң… Test services first (IA, Supabase, etc)
- вң… Mock Supabase (nГЈo use DB real em testes)

